Why Choose Us

No Minimum Order

Buy only one car? That's totally OK. We figure out shipping and custom clearance for you. Buy more than one? Very welcome, you are the boss.

Huge Product Variety

Covered the most popular vehicles in China. For VIP customers, tell us what you want, and we do our best find it for you.

Affordable Price

Limited budge but want a good car? You are lucky, that's what we are good at. Car Price* starts from CNY 30,000 (around 4,000 USD$, crazy, I know). Talk to our sales team, find the best model for you.

*: Exclude Shipping fee and Tax. Shipping fee depends on your location, we do our best to decrease the shipping fee and tax by using duty-free port and the nearest car source.

High Quality Vehicles

We only pick the best quality car company as our partner. We assure you that the car you see online is as good as it is. You have my word. Or you know what? Let's arrange a video call, I'll show you what we got.

Global Shipping Guarantee

Following the Belt and Road Initiative, nowadays China is doing its best on international shipping, especially for the Central Asia, Middle East and Europe customers. The connections between our countries are strong, so as our business. We shpping to you via train, road or ship, depends on the cost and time efficiency.

Design is Thinking Made Visual

Our Story

Since 1997

Dalian Dadong Automotive Service Co., Ltd. is a comprehensive automotive sales and service enterprise, established on November 22, 2009. The company provides a range of services including vehicle maintenance and repair, bodywork and painting, used car sales, and new car sales. Its origins can be traced back to Dadong Automotive Motorcycle Repair, established in 1997, and Dadong Automotive Beauty Service Department, established in 2003, giving the company a history of 26 years. Dadong Automotive has always revolved around the development of China's automotive and motorcycle industry, steadily growing and achieving remarkable results.

Present Days

Dalian Dadong Automotive Service Co., Ltd. has earned the trust and praise of its customers with its years of experience, expertise, and keen insight into customer needs. The company not only provides high-quality automotive maintenance and repair services but also offers a wide range of used cars and new cars for customers to choose from. Whether buying a used car or selecting a new car, customers can find their ideal vehicle at Dadong Automotive.

Core Values

The company's mission is to pursue the material and spiritual well-being of all partners and to warm the world through love and service to customers. To achieve this mission, Dadong Automotive adheres to the values of integrity in action and warm service. Integrity is the cornerstone of the company's development, requiring every employee to treat customers and partners with sincerity and honesty. Warm service is the company's commitment to customers, whether it is maintenance, repair, or sales, Dadong Automotive is dedicated to providing customers with a warm, thoughtful, and professional service experience.

Our Community

As an integrated automotive sales and service company, Dadong Automotive not only focuses on customer needs but also actively gives back to society. The company actively participates in public welfare activities, providing assistance and support to community residents. Dadong Automotive firmly believes that through sincere service and contributions to society, long-lasting and solid cooperative relationships can be established, creating more value for society.
